                    "line_text": "Et la terre maudite est comme un champ aride",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Où la ronce inféconde, et qu'on arrache en vain,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Dans le sillon qui brûle étouffe le bon grain.",
